\begin_layout Standard
OHReplay is an application for displaying Replay Frames.
 The nice thing is that OHReplay displays frames exactly as they have been
 displayed by the casino.
 That means that once a frame is displayed by OHReplay, you can connect
 OpenHoldem to that displayed frame just as if you were connecting to the
 native poker client window.
 This allows for easy debugging of your Table Map and bot logic while offline.
\end_layout

